{"tid":651930,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣訓練細貓唔好發癲搶野食","createTime":"2018-05-03T12:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T16:43:28.000Z","uid":128298,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc9b137424a7eae0ed25add17ab3657db23ae0d","tid":651930,"uid":128298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"屋企本身有隻歲幾大貓，佢一直好乖好冇問題<br />\n但呢排多左隻幾個月大貓仔，佢完全好似青山放出黎咁痴撚晒線，<br />\n平時搶晒大貓啲野食都算，我分開餵，<br />\n但大貓行近啲睇佢食咩都要「胡」佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打邊爐佢跳上枱一口擔走晒啲蝦走，啲熟豬肉點左豉油佢又照擔走，<br />\n我衝埋去想係佢個口拎返舊肉佢好惡咁「胡」我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最on9係我有時開薯片佢都要走黎搶放入口想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我見過佢食粒貓砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬左一啖發現唔食得就吐返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢完全好似前世未近食過野咁，又唔識好似其他貓咁聞下啲野先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底呢隻痴線佬我可以點教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/205435_94ce5549eb79ebdc305f77f7ebd6857a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F205435_94ce5549eb79ebdc305f77f7ebd6857a.png&h=eaae6781&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8b2ae8ff0d38b1ea6745131196d431dcfc20707","tid":651930,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"細貓係咪浪浪執返黎養？"},{"pid":"382d0eed5b03f4f7ec3b6fc3f6c3b3a5612ae327","tid":651930,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8b2ae8ff0d38b1ea6745131196d431dcfc20707","tid":651930,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"細貓係咪浪浪執返黎養？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"因為睇佢好瘦咁。似有過可怕經歷驚無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131dfb3daf17de543020eed7e0831e9e801ebb8e","tid":651930,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁對埋主子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c3610754ffd472101d882c2775b056eda8978b","tid":651930,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"留名 貓好難教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225986256882763c7c0a992b60325b7b4e5b6b36","tid":651930,"uid":128298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"佢又唔驚水<br />\n冇得用噴水黎罰佢 <br />\n鬧佢又唔驚<br />\n用咩方法先教到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31123857b354a39014489696ab843738617db518","tid":651930,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢又唔驚水<br />\n冇得用噴水黎罰佢 <br />\n鬧佢又唔驚<br />\n用咩方法先教到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忍心鎖佢入籠養一排就會純<br />\n同埋要鬧同輕打<br />\n佢一搶嘢食就要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}